are nested (`models/unets/`, `models/transformers/`, `models/autoencoders/`, …) — the `**` glob is
intentional. Scaffold by comparison rather than from memory — copy the closest reference and follow
`.ai/models.md` for the per-class attributes, attention pattern, and gotchas:
